import pygame

# pygame setup
pygame.init()
screen = pygame.display.set_mode()
clock = pygame.time.Clock() 
running = True 
while running:
    for event in pygame.event.get(): 
        if event.type == pygame.QUIT: 
            running = False 
    
    screen.fill("purple")
